name: Vintage Mother Mary Heart Necklace
description:
A vintage necklace created from found pieces of old jewelry and made into a new necklace ready to be worn and loved.


Handmade. One of a kind.

Chain measures 12 inches. Charm adds additional 2 inches.

Have a nice day.

name: Vintage Findings Charm Bracelet
description:
This charm bracelet features unique pieces of old jewelry re-discovered and re-created into a new bracelet for you to love and cherish.

Completely unique and one of a kind.

Bracelet measures 8 inches long

name: Wish
description:
Stamped "wish" necklace - completely sterling silver products except the wish charm which is pewter.  The round disk has texture for interest.

One of a kind.  Handmade by me.

Chain measures 9inches long, charm is 3/4" = 9 3/4" total length.

name: grandma's jewels
description:
Wearing your grandma's jewelry is cool again with this fabulous necklace created from vintage jewelry.  Features 6 different styles and colors of pearls.  It is one of a kind and completely unique.  A great addition to any jewelry collection.

Measures approximately 17 inches long.

name: elephant parade
description:
A handmade necklace on knotted wax cord NO clasp, easily slips over your head.

Contains unique charms in gold, silver, and bronze including a cute little miniature elephant. An opaque blue bead accompanies the charms.

Real swarovski crystals above the charms accent this beautiful cluster.


Necklace measures 13 1/2 inches and 15 total inches with charms.
